notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-17T21:31:25.688Z",maintainer-agent,"Origin context preserved: discovered during PR #580 when a test assumed pm_deps options.dep mutates. The pm-qxwu top-level warning mechanism (TOOL_DECLARED_KEYS at tools/call) is the intended pattern to extend one level into options objects using the per-action optional lists in tool-schema.ts as the contract source."
